keyFacts: The document is an email dated July 13, 2020, concerning a report on Ghislaine Maxwell.
A U.S. Pretrial Services Officer Specialist in the Southern District of New York is sending a corrected final report, indicating ongoing legal administrative activity in her case.
The prior version of the report contained minor typos with some dates, prompting this correction.
